The President Is Being Hunted By Aliens | Alien Invasion + The Day The Earth Stopped | Hollywood 2024 Blockbuster Action Movie 

Alien Invasion - After an alien spacecraft destroys Washington, D.C., the residents of a small town must fight off a unit of alien soldiers on the hunt for the President of the United States and the mysterious device he's carrying after his escape chopper crash lands nearby.

2018.  Stars: Arielle Hader, Matthew Pohlkamp, Christina Licciardi

The Day The Earth Stopped - Hundreds of massive intergalactic robots appear in all of the world's major capitals with an ultimatum: Prove the value of human civilization or be destroyed.

2008.  Stars: C. Thomas Howell, Judd Nelson, Darren Dalton
